#tellraw @s [{"text":"<Xil> ","color":"white","italic":false},{"text":"People call me Xil. It's... a little dumb, but it wasn't my choice. I'm not interested in telling you why. But what you should know is that I'm not who I once was, in case you've heard the stories. ...You haven't? I see. Well, I'll be the first to tell you that ignorance is bliss. Anyway, I'm after something very sacred. Not to steal it, but to destroy it! I know what it is, and unlike many people that also know, I'm actually strong enough to deal with it, and what might come after doing so. After all, I did serve ","color":"yellow","font":"rr_recast:impatience"},{"text":"[REDACTED]","color":"dark_red","font":"minecraft:default"},{"text":", so I know my way around combat. Just don't get in my way, and you'll be fine.","color":"yellow","font":"rr_recast:impatience"}]
#
#tellraw @s [{"text":"<Glavier> ","color":"white","italic":false},{"text":"Ah, hello. I am Glavier Benevue. I once served Kalekadvia as a Royal Guardsman. However, as I'm sure you know, that has long since come to pass. ...what do you mean by this? You don't know anything about Kalekadvia? That is a rather humorous joke. But on a more serious matter, I am now accompanying Xil here as he travels Seder. I do know what it is that he's after, but I am slightly fearful of his methods... or at least, I would be if I could be. I am unable to feel emotion or express it in any form, due to a curse that I needed placed on me after... well, the events at Kalekadvia. Even now, all these years later, I still have little control over how I might behave if I was to... uh, well, I'll not bore you with those details. But don't fret, the curse is rather strong. It was placed upon me by a powerful ritualist, she served ","color":"dark_aqua","font":"rr_recast:indifference"},{"text":"[REDACTED]","color":"dark_red","font":"minecraft:default"},{"text":", and after her aid I came to serve under the same master. Much like Xil, I grew to become much more powerful through the trainings and teachings I underwent, and now I feel confident that I can provide my aid to all of Seder when needed.","color":"dark_aqua","font":"rr_recast:indifference"}]
#
#tellraw @s [{"text":"<Alkhin> ","color":"white","italic":false},{"text":"Hello there! My name is Alkhin Sinclaire, and I'm the Headmistress of the Fhuldriem Dragonkin clan. It's a pleasure to meet you! I suppose you might be wondering why I am accompanying such... interesting characters, when I could be home with my family and friends. Well, it's come to our attention that a lot of Seder has been overrun with odd Chaos energy, or at least more odd than usual, and as a member of the Dragonkin clan, we have a deep-rooted connection to the magic of this world. It sorta means our clan is indirectly threatened by even a slight anomaly, but this is a far stranger anomaly than we've ever seen before. So here we are! It's a pretty large undertaking for someone as young as I am, but I am very determined to find out the root of this strangeness and solve it. ...Wait what did you say?? You haven't heard of Dragonkin before?? Well that's... uh, pretty surprising... Where did you say you were from again?","color":"green","font":"rr_recast:impedence"}]
#tellraw @s [{"text":"<Alkhin> ","color":"white","italic":false},{"text":"Oh, you said you wanted a demonstration of some of my \"draconic\" abilities? This may be a good start, let me show you some of the Draconic language of my people... Be careful though, because this is part of how we control magic. I'll just demonstrate a simple Light spell:","color":"green","font":"rr_recast:impedence"},{"text":"\nAlkhin draws a deep breath, her horn glows dimly and her eyes shine in tandem...\n","color":"gray","font":"minecraft:default"},{"text":"<Alkhin> ","color":"white","italic":false,"font":"minecraft:default"},{"text":"GUIDING LIGHT","color":"light_purple","font":"rr_recast:draconic"}]

